# ğŸ¬ Movie Search Bot

A simple web app that fetches and displays movie details using the OMDb API.

## ğŸš€ Features

- Search for any movie by title
- Displays poster, release year, genre, actors, and IMDb rating
- Clean, responsive UI with card layout

## ğŸ› ï¸ Technologies Used

- HTML5, CSS3 (Responsive styling)
- JavaScript (ES6+)
- Axios (for API requests)
- OMDb API

## ğŸ”§ How It Works

1. User enters a movie name and clicks "Search".
2. The app sends a request to the OMDb API using Axios.
3. The response is parsed, and a styled card with movie info is shown.

## ğŸ“¦ Setup Instructions

1. Clone or download the repository.
2. Open `index.html` in your browser.
3. Make sure you have internet access to load Axios from CDN.

## ğŸŒ API Used

- [OMDb API](http://www.omdbapi.com/)

